🔹 LIGHT 💡
✋ Open hand → ON ✅ (easy)
✊ Fist → OFF ✅ (easy)
🔄 Hand rotation → change color ⚠️ (possible but harder)
🤏 Pinch (thumb + index) → brightness ✅ (good choice)
🔹 MUSIC 🎵
✊ Fist → Pause ✅
✋ Open → Play ✅
🔁 Circle with 1 finger → loop ⚠️ (hard, not reliable)
👉 Swipe right → Next ✅
👈 Swipe left → Previous ✅
✋✋ Two hands:
Left hand swipe left → –10s ⚠️ (medium)
Right hand swipe right → +10s ⚠️ (medium)
🔹 TV 📺
✋ Open → ON ✅
✊ Fist → OFF ✅
🔹 FAN 🌬️
🔄 Hand rotation → ON ⚠️ (same issue as light)
✊ Fist → OFF ✅
🔹 WHITEBOARD 📷
🤏🤏 Two-hand “snap gesture” → capture ⚠️ (hard, unreliable)
